data.description: Welcome to this beautifully updated single story home!  This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a professionally converted garage that can be utilized as an fourth bedroom or additional living space. The home offers a nice open floor plan allowing the Living area to flow nicely into the Kitchen. Several tasteful updates were done to this home giving it a fresh modern look! It is conveniently located near several schools, restaurants and dining.
